{
  "stem": "18061.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I started working $15 a week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I thank-- thank god we didn't need nothing from nobody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't get anything from nobody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We weren't-- we wasn't supported, not by a jury, not by the Jewish Federation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was called to be a witness of the one that was the first one-- it was, if I'm not mistaken, 1951 of a trial from a man from the Treblinka extermination camp by the name of Josef Hirtreiter.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That trial was in Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I testified to that time, first thing, in Germany was a little simple like it is here in the United States.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the United States, they bring the men in front.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He sits next to the judge or what.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Over there, when I came in, we were about five, six witnesses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Over-- I just-- I just say what I-- when it-- what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I came into trial, the judge ask your name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So and so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You are a witness for this and this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Will you recognize the man?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's quite a few years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No, he said, do you see the man here?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The man sit in middle of the public.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's 500, 600 people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wears civil clothes like anybody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the eyes you can never forget.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I pointed out at him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [? they ?] callled him in on the bench.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time I-- I testified.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another time I was over this in Dusseldorf against 10 or 11 from Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of them in court, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Franz ?] [NON-ENGLISH] was [NON-ENGLISH], was [NON-ENGLISH], was-- I don't remember all the name of that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, the same thing we testified.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were find guilty.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
